body:
Bumps [syn](https://github.com/dtolnay/syn) from 1.0.81 to 1.0.82.
Release notes

Sourced from syn's releases.

1.0.82

  • Support parenthesized generic argument syntax with :: disambiguator: Fn::() -> ! (#1096)
Commits
  • 5697be5 Release 1.0.82
  • 809ab0f Merge pull request #1099 from dtolnay/coloncolonparen
  • ef11688 Parse parenthesized path arguments with disambiguator
  • 8648f5a Add test for parenthesized path arguments with disambiguator
  • c859588 Install newest build of cargo-outdated
  • ce9ded7 Update test suite to nightly-2021-11-13
  • 3978948 Update test suite to nightly-2021-11-08
  • 39ac201 Clippy if_then_panic lint has been renamed to manual_assert
  • See full diff in compare view
